Anne Lockhart (actress) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Anne_Lockhart_(actress) 0 Anne Kathleen Maloney (born September 6, 1953), known professionally as Anne Lockhart, is an American actress best known for her role as Lieutenant Sheba in the original Battlestar Galactica series. She is the daughter of actress June Lockhart.
